---
layout: layout.njk
title: Best AI Tools for UK Electricians
---
<section class="space-y-4">
  <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Category Hub</p>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950">Best AI Tools for UK Electricians</h1>
  <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-700">
    Practical, no-hype guides for UK electricians. We focus on tools that reduce admin,
    speed up quoting, improve customer communication, and support safe on-site work.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="mt-10">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Start Here</h2>
  <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-4">
    {% for post in collections.electricians | reverse %}
      <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
        <a class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 hover:underline" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
